#DISCLOSURE

As the creators of CertifyMe Google Form Add-on, we want to ensure our users that we adhere to Google's Limited Use requirements and API Services User Data Policy.
Any data obtained through the Google APIs will only be used for issuing certificates via our add-on and will not be shared with third-party applications. 
